* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈɔɹ.ɡən.ɪ.zəm/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{biology}} A discrete and complete [[living]] thing, such as [[animal]], [[plant]], [[fungus]] or [[microorganism]].
# {{context|by extension}} Any [[complex]] thing with properties normally associated with living things.

